OL,4,Ccertificate 'with Israel scribbled out'
OL,6,FThe Home Office said it will launch an
OL,7,Finvestigation into a baby's birth
OL,8,Fcertificate that was reportedly
OL,9,Freturned to the parents with the word
OL,10,F"Israel" scribbled out.
OL,12,FA man had sent off a passport
OL,13,Fapplication for his six-month-old baby
OL,14,Fgirl, charity Campaign Against
OL,15,FAntisemitism posted on X, formerly
OL,16,Fknown as Twitter, and the attached
OL,17,Fbirth certificate was returned ripped
OL,18,Fwith the word "Israel" crossed out.
OL,20,FThe parents are "very concerned" about
OL,21,Fthe incident, the charity added.
