OL,6,FHome Secretary James Cleverly replied
OL,7,Fto the social media post saying that
OL,8,Fthe Home Office would investigate what
OL,9,Fhad happened.
OL,11,F"I have asked my officials to
OL,12,Finvestigate this urgently and will see
OL,13,Fthat appropriate action is taken," he
OL,14,Fwrote.
OL,16,FThe Home Office hasn't yet responded
OL,17,Fto ITV News' request for comment.
